{
  "texts": [
    "Our empirical research investigated explainable social media recommendations from a user perspective.",
    "There are several limitations of our study.",
    "Firstly, explainable recommendations are a relatively new concept, and lay users are primarily unaware of possible algorithmic explanation features being introduced on social media.",
    "This study does not capture the long-term perception of explainable social media recommendations.",
    "Secondly, this study does not explore the end users' perception based on different types of explanations, such as textual, visual, or hybrid explanations."
  ]
}